  ¡§Li7-li7, kin-a2-jit8 lan2 oe7-thang chiah8 khah ho2 e5 mih8!¡¨ Beh jip8 tiam3 e5 si5 Pek-jim2 chiu7 an2-ni kong2. In saN-kap che7 ti7 phou2-thong in teh che7 khah lai7-bin7 e5 toh. Pek-jim2 chiu7 kio3 su7-hau7 e5 gin2-na2 lai5. ¡§ChhiaN2 li2 chit-tng3 ka7 goan2 ke-thiN chit8-boe2 hi5 hou7 goan2.¡¨ 
