  U7 chit8-pai2 in teh kang-chok e5 si5, Pek-jim2 u7 thiaN-tioh8 chit8 e5 hu7-jin5 lang5 an2-ni kong2, 
  ¡§Chit-e5 gin2-na2 chin-chiaN3 sui2, chin kho2-ai3, chhin-chhiuN7 thiN-sai3 e5 khoan2!¡¨ 
  Hit chit8-mi5 saN-kap ki5-to2 liau2, A-hoa jip8 bin5 e5 si5 Pek-jim2 chiu7 pang-chan7 A-hoa kah phoe7, i che7 ti7 A-hoa e5 chhng5, thiaN A-hoa teh khun3 peng5-an e5 hoaN5-siaN, lai5 siuN7-tioh8 hit-e5 hu7-jin5-lang5 sou2 kong2 e5 oe7. I chiu7 chhun-chhiu2 bong A-hoa e5 thau5-khak. ¡§Siat-su2 goa2 na7 u7 bak8-chiu, goa2 chiu7 oe7-thang khoaN3 li2 e5 bin7!¡¨ I e5 chhiu2 chiu7 bong i e5 bin7, phiN7, bak8-chiu kap chhui3-phoe2. ¡§Li7-li7, li2 sit8-chai7 chin kho2-ai3! Li2 si7 goa2 e5 sio2 thiN-sai3! Li2 si7 goa2 bang7-siong2 tiong e5 thiN-sai3!¡¨ Pek-jim2 chim i e5 thau5-hiah8. I e5 bak8-chiu u7 bak8-sai2. 
  ¡§Goa2 it-chhe3 e5 phaiN2-bang7 long2 soah lah! M7-si7 u7 sim2-mih8 se3-kan e5 toa7-su7, chi2-u7 li2 e5 chhut-hian7 hou7 goa2 e5 it-chhe3 long2 toa7 pian3-oaN7.¡¨ 
